rows.label: qst650202_msg0001
rows.name:
What kind of a person would stand
around waiting in a place like this?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0002
rows.name:
All of Bahn's accomplices were rounded
up, but this stinks of his handiwork.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0003
rows.name: That letter was suspicious, all right.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0004
rows.name:
Hana hate to say it, but this feel
like trap.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0005
rows.name: I been waiting for this moment, Tora.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0006
rows.name: Who that?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0007
rows.name: Meh-ho-hoo!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0008
rows.name: Hup!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0009
rows.name: M...my back...

rows.label: qst650202_msg0010
rows.name:
Who you?
Why you send Tora letter?
Why you want Blade data?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0011
rows.name:
Tora, dear littlepon.
You not recognise me?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0013
rows.name:
I Senzo.
Grampypon of Tora!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0016
rows.name: Pull other wing, it got bells on.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0017
rows.name: Meh meh?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0018
rows.name:
D-did Tora forget voice and face
of old Grampypon?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0019
rows.name:
You look similar but there no way
you the real deal!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0020
rows.name: Grampypon was killed by Muimui!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0021
rows.name: Meh meh meh?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0022
rows.name:
Tora not believe me...sad day indeed.
Feels like Senzo might faint.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0023
rows.name:
Tora... Are you sure this isn't
your grandad?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0024
rows.name:
Grampypon is dead as doornail.
Besides, Grampypon better at writing
than this imposter.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0025
rows.name:
That sad effect of injury from Muimui.
Limbs no longer move with grace of
younger years.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0027
rows.name:
Plausibility level of story increased
to unexpected levels.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0028
rows.name: Tora still not believe.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0029
rows.name:
First Dad alive, now somehow
Grampypon alive too? Life not that
easy or convenient!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0030
rows.name: Meh meh...

rows.label: qst650202_msg0031
rows.name: There nothing for it.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0032
rows.name:
This risky move but Tora has forced
my hand. There is proof that Senzo
who he say he is.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0033
rows.name: What proof?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0034
rows.name:
Search in roots of Saffronia tree in
Gwenith Paddies, near Invidian
capital Fons Maim.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0035
rows.name:
What you dig up there will prove
that I telling the truth.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0036
rows.name:
It seems like the only way.
Shall we head there, Tora?

rows.label: qst650202_msg0038
rows.name: Masterpon, let's go!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0039
rows.name: Fine.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0040
rows.name:
But... If this "proof" no good for
convince us, we not come back here!

rows.label: qst650202_msg0041
rows.name: That okay.

rows.label: qst650202_msg0042
rows.name: Take care, Tora...
